title.rendered: TAMBOURINE HONORED TO RECEIVE MULTIPLE TRAVEL WEEKLY MAGELLAN AWARDS

content.rendered:
FT. LAUDERDALE, Fla., Oct. 24, 2023 /PRNewswire/ — Tambourine, the Fort Lauderdale-headquartered digital marketing technology company serving hotels, resorts, and tourism destinations worldwide, is celebrating thirteen Travel Weekly Magellan Award wins with its clients.

The Travel Weekly Magellan Awards honor the best in everything travel, from property design and airline experiences to marketing strategy and new travel technology, shedding light on the passionate professionals who make it all happen.

Originally published at https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/tambourine-honored-to-receive-multiple-travel-weekly-magellan-awards-301966180.html
Images courtesy of https://pixabay.com
